-- Rule #8 retirement: the write protocol verifies claimed-novel ids
-- in-transaction and bulk-COPYs directly (NpgsqlWorkingSetApply); the period
-- fold runs client-side against the same native glicko-2
-- (NpgsqlConsensusFold). The server-side apply/fold entry points below have
-- no callers and are dropped on upgrade.
DROP FUNCTION IF EXISTS laplace_apply_batch(text);
DROP FUNCTION IF EXISTS consensus_fold_partition_incremental(text, boolean);
